metadata.description:
The feeling of "the wait is over" is one of the best feelings in the world, isn't it?

"Waiting" is one of the records I made while in the US this past July of 2022, I was super inspired, but at the same time with a bittersweet kinda feeling. While I was able to meet a lot of friends from the internet in real life, I also wasn't able to play many shows I would have wanted to play. Felt like i was waiting for something to happen so i could start playing those shows, and I had to put my feelings into the music. 

I've been also "waiting" for this spot at Sound.xyz for a while, so I'm stoked it's finally time for my genesis drop here in this amazing platform!

This is also me trying to show everyone the new vibe I've got coming for 2023. Trappy, but Poppy, but weird, but mainstream.

Hopefully this track will make someone smile. Or get angry! 

Expect more music dropping here soon-

Love,
Dabow.
metadata.name: Waiting #1
